title: History of versions Kubernetes
pageDescription: The VK Cloud Solutions platform provides several versions of Kubernetes, which can be used in cloud clusters.Here you will find a detailed story of Kubernetes versions that are supported or supported in the past.Each version presents: a brief description of the changes in the VK Cloud service and in Kubernetes itself.
shortDescription: The history of Kubernetes versions that are supported or supported in the past for VK Cloud Solutions clusters
